title: Hour 2 - NBA Draft Preview, Dan Wetzel

Dan runs down the story lines for tonight's NBA Draft and talks to Dan Wetzel about NFL Commissioner Roger Goodell's testimony in front of Congress regarding Daniel Snyder and the Washington Commanders.
